Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:06.42,Narration,,0,0,0,,Actually, Kokkuri-san has a certain weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:08.98,Narration,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, when it comes to PCs, the internet or phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know how they work, so they scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a geezer left behind the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, you modern day girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been bad with stuff like that, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san, it'd be better if you keep up with the times a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even know how to record something on tv.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please record this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get serious, even I can record something!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna see how I record something with G-Code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Code is long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no VHS in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:10.15,Narration,,0,0,0,,Of course, Kokkuri-san doesn't know how to wire a tv either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bad with new devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So bad that I break out in hives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, check out my new smartphone, it's the latest gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly shove it in my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here! Feel free to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:40.64,Narration,,0,0,0,,In order to help Kokkuri-san overcome his weakness, \Nshe decided to surround him with smartphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay if you get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.50,Narration,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri-san couldn't keep up with the quickly evolving civilisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.70,Narration,,0,0,0,,But even though he is like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:18.32,Narration,,0,0,0,,he makes sure to buy new home appliances after some years of use.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:31.71,Narration,,0,0,0,,It is due to a bad experience, when an appliance he had been using for way too long burnt his tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:37.80,Narration,,0,0,0,,and because he is aware that switching to more recent eco appliances is economically advantageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,15,,No, it will still do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:49.18,Narration,,0,0,15,,But in the end, Kokkuri-san still is bad with new devices.
